{"tid":2511833,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯] 好多動漫人物其實一轉行就做硬世界冠軍，例如四驅兄弟 足球小將同男兒當入樽","createTime":"2021-05-01T08:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T08:23:14.000Z","uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10c167eb1e1c09d3a45615302cd3a6ea332cb8e1","tid":2511833,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">四驅兄弟</span></span>應該<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">轉行去跑馬拉松</span></strong></span>，場場賽車個幾鐘不斷當一百米咁追住架車，豪仔出麥林號龍捲風時仲可以一秒就追倒百幾米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcLK2VsJb51b4YhCrhEYkLXf7Ua4ctkcGUefReb3MxD1R?filename=BoHqmsv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoHqmsv.jpg&h=52212c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">足球小將</span></span></strong>就<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">轉行打NBA</span></strong></span>，個個跳高騰空能力幾十秒，仲有得三次轉身再射門，入到NBA連Michael Jordan 1988年入樽賽個球都可以死開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWKErAVS4BnbqfJoZX53tUokUgSshPzHPpCFpUznRFd9H?filename=NvThcDT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvThcDT.png&h=05b8bba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkclutch/videos/1524383457645875/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkclutch%2Fvideos%2F1524383457645875%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=d40d1b55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkclutch/videos/1524383457645875/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">男兒當入樽</span></strong></span><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>的櫻木</strong></span></span>就一定要<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">轉行打柔道</span></span></strong>，人地葉問一打十就做武術宗師，櫻木無練習過之下就一個打十一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT6vxANdPUsWvxqaow91Kac8Nr2akWupb4Mqqu7MoLxJn?filename=j3vGEDP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3vGEDP.png&h=56b52dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcYs1PEZjXZQn3p9RjKPHBenSt6r9veK535BrZLp3bxya?filename=TJiXXqM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJiXXqM.png&h=1953a323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他動漫人物介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d1562bdaffb0569bb4657d9870b91f35be2523e7","tid":2511833,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"264006dc0f3ae649064c6d2ce80a2e3551aa31f3","tid":2511833,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"網球王子班人應該去當兵"},{"pid":"06514ad9c372355dede46143f24eaa9dbb89ec0b","tid":2511833,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"櫻木入柔道部實可以稱霸全國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}